 编码变体（如 `..%2f`、`%2e%2e%2f`），并限制对敏感目录的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95730430727064&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/699","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19540"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0929.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0928","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0928.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1082","title":"T. Hauck Jana WebServer 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Jana WebServer 1.0至1.46版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制的\"......\"（变形点点攻击）请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用方式简单，影响t. hauck Jana代理Web服务器的多个版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1082"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.017","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 Jana WebServer 1.40，厂商已不再提供安全更新。建议立即停止使用该产品，迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。如无法立即替换，可在反向代理或 WAF 层过滤包含连续点号（如 `......`）等目录遍历特征的 URL 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93941794201059&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/699","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1082.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1082","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1082.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1082.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-57hw-cwh6-33rc/GHSA-57hw-cwh6-33rc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1082.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000820.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b38e6c00-7918-40e7-b279-5fa6ce0d244b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0928.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0616","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0616.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0830","title":"SCO UnixWare 7.0/7.0.1/7.1 Xsco 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.0、7.0.1 及 7.1 版本中自带的 Xsco 程序存在基于堆栈的缓冲区溢出漏洞。该产品以 root 权限运行，本地普通用户可通过构造超长的命令行参数触发溢出，覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而提升自身权限至 root，危害系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0830"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1999-10-08","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"安装 SCO 官方发布的安全补丁（如 UnixWare 7 的 ptf 包），或升级至已修复该问题的 UnixWare 7.1.1 及后续版本。临时措施可移除 Xsco 程序的 setuid root 位权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T15:26:05.741201112+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0830","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/736"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19498"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0616.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1158","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1158.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1522","title":"Roxen Web Server htmlparse.pike 递归解析漏洞","description":"Roxen Web Server 1.3.11 及更早版本中，htmlparse.pike 组件在处理 RXML 页面的 referer 标签时存在缺陷，可能与递归解析逻辑相关。远程攻击者可通过构造包含特制 referer 标签或递归 RXML 结构的恶意请求发送至目标服务器，触发解析异常，可能导致拒绝服务或异常行为。该漏洞影响使用受影响版本 Roxen Web Server 的站点，攻击无需身份认证，仅需能向服务器发送 HTTP 请求即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1522"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:37.233","remediation":"建议立即升级 Roxen Web Server 至 1.3.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了 htmlparse.pike 递归解析和 RXML 中 referer 标签的漏洞。如无法立即升级，可暂时禁用 RXML 中的 referer 标签功能或限制 RXML 递归解析深度作为临时缓解措施。建议从 Roxen 官方网站下载最新版本进行升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93942579008408&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d4a574a76aebe4c90e3ed9125b2a8b9cb55a2a89/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1522.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1522","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1522.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cd1e3d0adf029810963282884bd6480e52b853ac/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1522.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3vpv-5wr7-2hx5/GHSA-3vpv-5wr7-2hx5.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1522.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000819.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/49a3b38344e5fb98213c282604cbf48964f92580/1999.tsv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1158.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1158.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1158.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1064","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1064.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1347","title":"Red Hat Linux Xsession 安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本中的 Xsession 组件存在安全绕过漏洞。具有受限账户的本地用户可通过从 kdm 登录管理器启动 KDE、GNOME 或其他桌面环境，绕过 .xsession 文件的执行限制，从而获取非授权的桌面环境访问权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需要拥有本地账户且能够物理或远程登录系统，利用门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1347"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.813","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 6.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复 Xsession 脚本对 kdm 启动桌面环境的权限校验。如无法升级，可修改 /etc/X11/xdm/Xsession 脚本，在启动 kde/gnome 前增加用户权限检查逻辑，或限制 kdm 仅允许授权用户登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93942774609925&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1347","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1347.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9h2-mfx3-9xhg/GHSA-h9h2-mfx3-9xhg.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1347.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000818.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1064.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1063","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1063.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1346","title":"Red Hat Linux rlogin PAM 配置安全绕过漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本中 rlogin 的 PAM 配置文件存在安全绕过漏洞。由于 PAM 规则配置顺序不当，宽松规则位于严格规则之前，导致即使管理员通过 /etc/nologin 文件明确禁用了 rlogin 登录，攻击者仍可利用该配置缺陷绕过限制，通过 rlogin 服务远程访问目标系统。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1346"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.2 或更高版本，或手动修改 /etc/pam.d/rlogin 配置文件，将检查 /etc/nologin 的限制规则置于宽松规则之前，确保禁用 rlogin 的配置生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93942774609925&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1063.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1066","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1349","title":"Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 NFS 守护进程 nfsd.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 中的 NFS 守护进程 nfsd.exe 存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 111 端口发送设置了 URG（紧急）标志的特定 TCP 数据包，导致 nfsd.exe 消耗大量系统资源，最终使 NFS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者无需认证即可触发，但需网络可达目标主机。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1349"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.080","remediation":"该产品（Xlink Technology Omni-NFS/X Enterprise 6.1）已停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 NFS 服务器方案（如 Windows Server 原生 NFS 服务或第三方活跃维护的 NFS 软件）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 TCP/UDP 111 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并禁用 NFS 服务的 URG 标志包处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93923679004325&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hv9m-2rcj-rh9v/GHSA-hv9m-2rcj-rh9v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1349.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000816.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1066.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1074","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1074.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1357","title":"Netscape Communicator 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.04 至 4.7 版本（及可能其他版本）在多种 UNIX 操作系统中存在字符编码转换漏洞，程序将 0x8b 字符错误转换为 \"<\" 符号、0x9b 字符错误转换为 \">\" 符号。远程攻击者可通过向未过滤这些字符的 CGI 程序注入特制载荷，触发跨站脚本攻击，进而窃取用户会话 Cookie 或执行恶意操作。该漏洞影响运行 Netscape Communicator 的 UNIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1357"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.097","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 Netscape Communicator 4.04-4.7。由于该产品已于 2001 年终止支持，建议立即停止使用并迁移至 Firefox 等现代浏览器。同时，服务器端 CGI 程序应对用户输入中的 0x8b 和 0x9b 字符进行过滤或 HTML 转义编码，作为纵深防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93915331626185&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1357.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1357","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1357.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1357.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p87-h429-g84q/GHSA-5p87-h429-g84q.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1357.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83056/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7a390ce4-5ffd-46ef-9e54-bf361746db99.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_xss.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1074.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1074.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1062","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1062.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1345","title":"Auto_FTP Auto_FTP.pl 脚本不安全临时目录权限漏洞","description":"Auto_FTP 0.2 版本中的 Auto_FTP.pl 脚本将 /tmp/ftp_tmp 目录作为共享目录使用，且未设置安全的权限控制，导致本地攻击者可利用该不安全权限实施两种攻击：一是将任意文件放入该目录以发送至远程服务器，二是查看正在传输中的文件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Auto_FTP 0.2 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1345"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:14.563","remediation":"将 Auto_FTP 升级至 0.3 或更高版本，或手动修改 Auto_FTP.pl 脚本，将共享目录从 /tmp/ftp_tmp 改为仅允许授权用户访问的专用目录（如 /var/ftp/private），并设置目录权限为 750（所有者读写执行，组读执行，其他无权限）。如软件已停止维护，建议迁移至支持安全配置的替代 FTP 自动化工具（如 lftp 或 curl-based 脚本），并避免在 /tmp 等全局可写目录中存放传输中的文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93923873006014&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1345.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1345","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1345.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1345.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw5c-qccp-53r4/GHSA-jw5c-qccp-53r4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1345.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3d72da75-8cdd-4ba7-8b20-28ce8f9621cd.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ee9754343b23d8c0f998865ae48a5d400d72ba81/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1062.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1060","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1344","title":"Auto_FTP 0.2 配置文件明文存储凭据漏洞","description":"Auto_FTP 0.2 版本中的 Auto_FTP.pl 脚本存在安全设计缺陷，将用户登录凭据（用户名和密码）以明文形式存储在 auto_ftp.conf 配置文件中。攻击者若能够读取该配置文件，即可直接获取明文凭据，进而利用这些凭据进行未授权访问。该漏洞的攻击前提是攻击者已获得文件读取权限，属于信息泄露类漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1344"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-05","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Auto_FTP 0.2 已停止维护，建议立即迁移至支持加密凭据存储的 FTP 自动化工具（如 lftp 配合加密 .netrc 文件）。如无法替换，须将 auto_ftp.conf 配置文件权限严格限制为仅管理员可读（如 chmod 600），并避免在共享目录中存放该配置文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T13:16:36.996947766+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1988","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1988.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1542","title":"Linux RPMMail 邮件命令注入远程代码执行漏洞","description":"RPMMail 是一款用于接收和处理电子邮件的 Linux 程序，其 1.4 之前版本在解析邮件协议时存在命令注入漏洞。该程序在处理 SMTP 会话的 \"MAIL FROM\" 命令时，未对发件人地址中的特殊字符进行安全过滤与转义，直接将其拼接进后续的 shell 命令中执行。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向运行 RPMMail 的服务端发送一封在 \"MAIL FROM\" 命令中携带 shell 元字符（如分号、反引号、管道符等）的特制电子邮件，即可在目标系统上以程序运行权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响所有使用 RPMMail 1.4 之前版本的 Linux 系统，攻击条件仅为能够与目标邮件服务建立 SMTP 连接，利用方式简单且危害极大，可导致服务器被远程控制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1542"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:40.817","remediation":"立即升级 RPMMail 至 1.4 或更高版本，可从 ftp://reedycreek.com 下载 rpmmail-1.4-2.i386.rpm 进行更新。若无法升级，请移除 /home/rpmmail/rpmmail 的 SUID 权限（chmod 755 /home/rpmmail/rpmmail）或卸载该软件包，并在防火墙层面限制 25 端口的入站连接作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93915641729415&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93923853105687&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3353","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1542.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1542","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1542.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1542.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9wm7-qv7w-f74f/GHSA-9wm7-qv7w-f74f.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1542.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000811.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--86142d35-fed1-4d44-aeea-b5856001ce17.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1988.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1173","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1173.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1541","title":"Cactus Software Shell Lock 本地符号链接攻击文件篡改漏洞","description":"Cactus Software Shell Lock 的 shell-lock 功能存在临时文件符号链接漏洞，本地用户可通过创建符号链接指向目标 shell 文件，诱使程序在处理临时文件时读取或修改已被解码的 shell 文件，从而在 shell 文件执行前篡改其内容。该漏洞影响 Cactus Software Shell Lock 软件，攻击条件要求攻击者具备本地访问权限。攻击者可利用符号链接攻击读取敏感信息或修改已解码的 shell 脚本，进而实现权限提升或执行任意命令。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1541"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:40.697","remediation":"由于 Cactus Software Shell Lock 已停止维护，建议立即停止使用该工具，改用支持安全临时文件创建的替代方案（如 shc）。如无法替换，可在执行 shell-lock 前设置 umask 077 限制临时文件权限，并确保临时目录 /tmp 设置了粘滞位，同时移除 shell-lock 的 setuid 权限以防止权限提升。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93916168802365&w=2","http://www.atstake.com/research/advisories/1999/shell-lock.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3358","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1541.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1541","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1541.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1541.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hr9m-3c7j-qx9f/GHSA-hr9m-3c7j-qx9f.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87913/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1541.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/88abaf2eeb3005b068b70cbe8eaa4a45012b7606/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1173.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1112","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1454","title":"Macromedia Matrix 屏幕保护程序安全绕过漏洞","description":"Macromedia 公司开发的 \"The Matrix\" 屏幕保护程序在 Windows 95 系统中存在安全绕过漏洞。当系统启用了\"密码保护\"选项后，具有物理访问权限的攻击者只需按下键盘上的 ESC（Escape）键即可绕过密码验证提示，直接进入系统桌面。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需任何特殊工具或技术知识，攻击者仅需物理接触目标计算机即可实施攻击，严重威胁系统安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1454"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.500","remediation":"立即卸载 \"The Matrix\" 屏幕保护程序，改用 Windows 95 自带或经过安全验证的第三方屏保。如必须使用，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 等受支持的操作系统版本，并启用屏幕保护密码与自动锁定策略。在无法升级系统时，可通过物理安全措施（如锁定机箱、限制控制台访问）防止未授权接触。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93915027622690&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1112.toml"}]